title: CyberLink PowerDVD Ultra 13.0.3520 (keygen CORE) [ChingLiu]
description:
What's new in version 13.0.3520.58?

[DVD, Blu-ray, and Video file Playback]
- Enhances program stability when playing CPRM and DVD-VR content.
- Adds support for Blu-ray movie "Movie 43".
- Enhances program stability for certain MKV file playback based on user feedback.
[User Experience Enhancements]
- Removes any network connection to MoovieLive server when "Movie Info" feature is disabled

Operating Systems: Windows XP SP3, Windows Vista, Windows 7, Windows 8, Windows 8.1

Graphics Processor (GPU) - Blu-ray Disc, DVD, and TrueTheater HD/3D Playback
Intel HD Graphics, ATI Radeon HD 5000, NVIDIA GeForce 9500GT or above

* Note: We strongly recommend that you update your graphics card driver to the latest version. 3D display devices are required for TrueTheater 3D playback.

Languages : English, French, German, Italian, Spanish (European), Chinese Simplified, Chinese Traditional, Japanese, Korean, Russian, Portuguese
